Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_LEO>
I guess this town's still developing, but there's
nothing good to see here yet.

<NAME_MOB_LEO>
I have yet to find anything worthwhile around
here, but I guess the key to success is
persistence...

<NAME_MOB_LEO>
You know, I did see something good on a shelf
back there... Maybe I should've bought it when I
had the chance...

<NAME_MOB_LEO>
This town's full of neat things to buy! I found
something nice and rare today!

<NAME_MOB_LEO>
A lot of the traders' products are pretty hard to
come by, aren't they?

<NAME_MOB_LEO>
I'd like to see all the rare goods the world has to
offer.
